Text.val: Remove all TINV/NFIN rows where legal collection = 'Y'

SQL_STMT_U.val: select distinct TINV_DEBC_DEBC from :1/TINV where TINV_ADMNO = :2 and TINV_CLNTNO = :3 and TINV_MARKCODESPEC = :4 for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
Delete from :1/TINV where TINV_ADMNO = :2 and TINV_CLNTNO = :3 and TINV_LEGALCOLLECTION = 'Y'
Delete from :1/NFIN where NFIN_ADMNO = :2 and NFIN_CLNTNO = :3 and NFIN_LEGALCOLLECTION = 'Y' and NFIN_NFIR_NO = :4
